  schema:name "Dual Power" ;
  schema:description "Dual power is the strategy of building alternative institutions that meet real needs outside the structures of [the state](../../../terms/the-state.md) and capital, creating a lived alternative that makes existing power arrangements unnecessary rather than seizing them." ;
